title USER_CREATED Event

User Manager/PlatformUser -> Event Manager:Raise Event USER_CREATED.

Event Manager ->WalletManagerPluginRoot:Listen To USER_CREATED Event.

Event Manager ->BitcoinCryptoNetworkPluginRoot:Listen To USER_CREATED Event.

note right of WalletManagerPluginRoot:create default wallet.

note right of BitcoinCryptoNetworkPluginRoot:create crypto wallet.

note right of User Manager/PlatformUser:created when there is no user.

note right of User Manager/PlatformUser:requested by the user.